Through my contributions, I aim to bridge gaps in existing methodologies, enhance model generalization, and push the boundaries of what is achievable in both time series forecasting and human-centric computer vision tasks. My work is driven by a commitment to advancing the field and providing practical solutions that can be readily applied in real-world scenarios.

